2010-12-16  Ludovic Courtès  <ludo@gnu.org>

	Implement `(ice-9 threads)' high-level constructs in terms of futures.
	* module/ice-9/threads.scm (parallel, par-mapper): Rewrite in terms of
	  `future' and `touch'.

