	Nuke GOOPS `Quick Start' section, in favour of the `Tutorial'
	These sections are pretty similar in aim, but `Tutorial' is mostly
	better material.

	* doc/ref/goops-tutorial.texi (Class definition): Add a sentence about
	  what slots are.

