	* libguile/Makefile.am (version.h): Delete target.
	  (EXTRA_DIST): Remove version.h.in.
	  (BUILT_SOURCES): Remove version.h.
	  (MOSTLYCLEANFILES): Remove version.h, version.h.tmp.
