2010-02-15  Ludovic Courtès  <ludo@gnu.org>

	Fix builds of `i18n.c' on non-GNU systems.
	* libguile/i18n.c (chr_to_case, str_to_case): Add `func_name' argument
	  and `FUNC_NAME' macro.  Update callers.

	Add `getaddrinfo' test.
