	* test-suite/Makefile.am (SCM_TESTS): Add `tests/vlist.test'.

	* benchmark-suite/Makefile.am (SCM_BENCHMARKS): Add
	  `benchmarks/vlists.bm'.

	* doc/ref/api-compound.texi (VLists, VHashes): New nodes.

