2009-07-31  Ludovic Courtès  <ludo@gnu.org>

	Add unused variable analysis in the tree-il->glil compiler.
	* module/language/tree-il/analyze.scm (<binding-info>): New record type.
	  (report-unused-variables): New procedure.

