	Merge branch 'syncase-in-boot-9'
	Conflicts:
		module/Makefile.am

2009-05-28  Ludovic Courtès  <ludo@gnu.org>

	Import R6RS bytevectors and I/O ports from Guile-R6RS-Libs 0.2.
	* README: Document dependency on GNU libunistring.

