	* libguile/gc.c (scm_permanent_object): Use `scm_gc_protect_object ()'.
	  (scm_gc_register_root): Do nothing.
	  (scm_init_storage): Removed initialization of `scm_permobjs' and
	  `scm_gc_register_roots'.

