	* libguile/hashtab.c (scm_i_rehash): Don't invoke
	  `SCM_HASHTABLE_DECREMENT ()' when a weak pair is encountered in the
	  source bucket.

	git-archimport-id: lcourtes@laas.fr--2005-libre/guile-core--boehm-gc--1.9--patch-43

